<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Please help me,,]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=4426&amp;p=18541#p18541"><![CDATA[
Classic Shell may not be loading at startup. Just create a shortcut to C:\Program Files\Classic Shell\ClassicStartMenu.exe and copy-paste it in your Startup folder at C:\Users\&lt;your user name&gt;\AppData\Roaming\Microsoft\Windows\Start Menu\Programs\Startup. Next time you shutdown, it will load automatically.<br /><br />Google Translation:<br />Classic Shell kan ikke læsning ved opstart. Bare oprette en genvej til C: \ Program Files \ Classic Shell \ ClassicStartMenu.exe og copy-paste det i mappen Start på C: \ Brugere \ &lt;dit brugernavn&gt; \ AppData \ Roaming \ Microsoft \ Windows \ Start Menu \ Programs \ Start. Næste gang du shutdown, vil den indlæse automatisk.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=54">Gaurav</a> — Thu Apr 02, 2015 5:22 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
</entry>
